metadata.name: Into the Neverwhere | Intro
metadata.description:
Well, good Stranger, you finally got lost.
There’s no way home, no future, no past. Just endless pure Neverwhere. Does it mean you destroyed to your bones or absolutely free to chose any fate you want? You decide.
I just came to show you that Neverwhere gives you truly freedom. Don’t be afraid, listen to yourself and follow your heart whatever it takes.
